{"tid":663510,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日檔案 生老病死","createTime":"2018-05-13T11:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T11:48:56.000Z","uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb5475c7de59be1eb601983e7bfc4091e024247","tid":663510,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"生老病死，是人生必經階段，當生命來到最後一段路，你可有想過，自己可以死在哪裡嗎？根據法例，要在家離世，必須有醫生於離世兩周前探視，並於病者去世當日親身上門簽發死亡證，否則就要送入急症室或報警處理。姚婆婆十年前患上乳癌，三年前復發，多次進出醫院，醫生指其壽命以「日」計，姚婆婆是佛教徒，希望離世後，能有人為她助念八小時，完成往生的佛教儀式。她決意離開醫院，回家接受紓緩治療，並由女兒照顧，直到臨終。"},{"pid":"c9384f8e988c6881aa00407e153595ad1eeaeaf3","tid":663510,"uid":73575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"一影呀婆就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86ced5288f7fb138cc56531e1d1cb6884080630","tid":663510,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9384f8e988c6881aa00407e153595ad1eeaeaf3","tid":663510,"uid":73575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"一影呀婆就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0c84a3ee4b5c6fd3ad401dd54a13d3ebf37791","tid":663510,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"終有一日都到自己"},{"pid":"fa45897113fbfc05d64cda689243ee1b23cfa566","tid":663510,"uid":140140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"個家庭應該係中產以上囉<br />\n平常人點做到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5857294f49787df44147509785914ef3871b859","tid":663510,"uid":69794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d0c84a3ee4b5c6fd3ad401dd54a13d3ebf37791","tid":663510,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"終有一日都到自己"},